{"tid":326483,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得當拿奴馬好蠢","createTime":"2017-07-18T04:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T16:16:35.000Z","uid":108894,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83789b0c88fd5cdfdb541908be162278b9365841","tid":326483,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:49:59.000Z","msg":"唔反對佢想去大球會，人望高處，有得揀邊個唔想去皇馬巴塞？<br />\n但問題係，佢只係一個岩岩出道嘅小將，只係打左一季好波，將來咩世界都唔知，貿然衝去皇馬又要隨時做拿華斯冇出場，到時成時生涯廢晒，點解唔留係AC米蘭練成熟D練好D手勢，過多兩三年再去皇馬，機會一定更加多<br />\n然而最撚過份嘅係，佢竟然為此拒絕續約，同球會撕破臉，咁就死得啦，如果球會因為咁擺落bench一年，甚至落預備組，冇機會出場，到時不論能力身價都大跌，不但自己冇錢賺，仲趕走好多有興趣嘅大球會，到時一係係AC米蘭虛耗歲月，一係被迫踢低級聯賽薪金同知名度大降<br />\n如果比我係當拿奴馬，一定盡快同球會公開道歉R份新約，以求自己可以穩定上陣，過兩三季先再考慮轉會。不過拉奧拿睇落都係一個只顧眼前利益嘅人，為左盡快令當拿奴馬轉會以賺取大筆佣金，佢一定極力勸當拿奴馬唔續約，今次當拿奴馬真係好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef0d279d3aae26c82d7ad5c2f53fcb35c2b301b","tid":326483,"uid":31848,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:52:37.000Z","msg":"潮"},{"pid":"b8b5ea813feebdc31d17f18e2102932c8ed073df","tid":326483,"uid":48162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:05:04.000Z","msg":"過多兩年跌watt 傷患都未定，到時搵鬼簽，有機會唔去幾時去"},{"pid":"f5c3305fdddf0edb58aa511a7510f5a6079d442c","tid":326483,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:05:29.000Z","msg":"坐左幾耐?"},{"pid":"baa9c49b16f940080fe9535047883eab62f64512","tid":326483,"uid":39508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:06:13.000Z","msg":"今年a米咁搞俾我都唔走住喇<br />\n之後真係踢得起到時點玩都得"},{"pid":"2512baeab6ad9ef56c9405f8789073462b1f1e45","tid":326483,"uid":33531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:07:52.000Z","msg":"唔係續左啦咩?"},{"pid":"9ae15151bf3f3b2563111bdd707dff458fe04ed4","tid":326483,"uid":39508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T05:09:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過多兩年跌watt 傷患都未定，到時搵鬼簽，有機會唔去幾時去</blockquote><br />\n去到踢唔起仲大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"298a3b67b3a3b05984b5b46285f8ba103afd3701","tid":326483,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:41:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過多兩年跌watt 傷患都未定，到時搵鬼簽，有機會唔去幾時去</blockquote><br />\n但亦唔覺得佢去皇馬可以坐穩正選<br />\n去次一級嘅球隊都唔係間間得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81dbeddc40e73836cf34ed66a2c1b9686749c1f1","tid":326483,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:42:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係續左啦咩?</blockquote><br />\n係就最好啦<br />\n佢真係未到轉會嘅時候"},{"pid":"a0a91053f5e98cfdf1c5b21da2be8ff78bb28097","tid":326483,"uid":60506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:44:01.000Z","msg":"樓主用ie上網，唔好怪佢"},{"pid":"f1059bdc1b6725e9cc445c146928ebada2867fff","tid":326483,"uid":48964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:45:24.000Z","msg":"入世未深，經理人太有機心又貪錢"},{"pid":"b619b526336751b6a19fcdc910e5c36f7d9fc918","tid":326483,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:46:32.000Z","msg":"温書好過啦"},{"pid":"a9104234827df85d63f65921802f223ca866488b","tid":326483,"uid":1265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:47:37.000Z","msg":"昏迷左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a458f500f65776441320ff3b3937ca16ff8dc9","tid":326483,"uid":47945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:49:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主用ie上網，唔好怪佢</blockquote><br />\n諗起幅圖笑鳩ie慢十怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9218d9cc971b8cb6636da4243df668f54d5c1af","tid":326483,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:58:05.000Z","msg":"一個月前嘅草稿？"},{"pid":"bac252f34ccdbb8780660b3d3caaeb27ca4c913a","tid":326483,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T07:26:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquo